{"artefact":[["_response_info",{"status":"ok"}],["title","Apply for a digital tachograph company smart card"],["id","https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/apply-for-a-digital-tachograph-company-smart-card.json"],["web_url","https://www.gov.uk/apply-for-a-digital-tachograph-company-smart-card"],["format","answer"],["details",{"need_id":"B987","business_proposition":true,"alternative_title":"How to apply for a digital tachograph company card","overview":"Contact DVLA to get a digital tachograph company smart card - change, replace, renew a card","updated_at":"2012-10-05T13:56:27+00:00","body":"\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>Apply to <abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr> for a digital tachograph company smart card.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>As an operator, you need a card to download data from the <a href=\"/tachographs/digital-tachographs\" title=\"Digital tachographs\">digital tachographs</a> in your vehicles. </p>\n\n<h2>How to apply</h2>\n\n<p>Complete application form D779B and post it to <abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr>. The address is on the form.</p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.dft.gov.uk/dvla/forms/~/media/pdf/forms/D779B.ashx\" title=\"Download an application for a digital tachograph company card (PDF, 120K)\">Download &lsquo;D779B - Application for a digital tachograph company card&rsquo; (PDF, 120KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<p>You can also use this form to:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>change the name or address on your cards</li>\n  <li>replace lost, stolen or damaged cards</li>\n  <li>renew expired cards</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>By post</h3>\n\n<p>You can <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.dvla.gov.uk/dvla/onlineservices/order_forms.aspx\" title=\"Ask DVLA to send you an application pack for a driver digital smart card.\">request an &lsquo;ST2A&rsquo; application pack in the post.</a></p>\n\n<h3>By phone</h3>\n\n<p>Call <abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr> for an &lsquo;ST2A&rsquo; application pack.</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong><abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Licensing Agency\">DVLA</abbr></strong> <br />\n0300 790 6109.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Northern Ireland</h2>\n\n<p>In Northern Ireland you can get application forms for company cards from the Driver &amp; Vehicle Agency (<abbr title=\"Driver &amp; Vehicle Agency\">DVA</abbr>). </p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong><abbr title=\"Driver &amp; Vehicle Agency\">DVA</abbr> licensing enquiries</strong><br />\n<a href=\"&#109;&#097;&#105;&#108;&#116;&#111;:&#100;&#118;&#108;&#110;&#105;&#064;&#100;&#111;&#101;&#110;&#105;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;\">&#100;&#118;&#108;&#110;&#105;&#064;&#100;&#111;&#101;&#110;&#105;&#046;&#103;&#111;&#118;&#046;&#117;&#107;</a><br />\n0845 402 4000</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>Visit <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.nidirect.gov.uk/digital-tachograph-company-cards\" title=\"Digital tachograph company cards in Northern Ireland\">nidirect</a> for more information.</p>\n\n"}],["tags",[{"title":"Drivers of lorries, buses and goods vehicles","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/driving%2Fdrivers-lorries-buses.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Includes tests, health and safety, roadside checks and carrying loads","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/with_tag.json?tag=driving%2Fdrivers-lorries-buses","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/driving/drivers-lorries-buses"},"parent":{"title":"Driving","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/driving.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Book your driving test or get a tax disc online, find out the legal requirements for buying, owning, importing or scrapping a car or motorcycle, and read about your rights and responsibilities as a driver.","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/with_tag.json?tag=driving","web_url":"https://ww